==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Marxism
<hw>Marx"ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A system of
economic and political thought, originated by <person>Karl
Marx</person>, and elaborated by others. It holds that the state has
been the a device for suppression of the masses, allowing exploitation
by a dominant (capitalistic) class; that historical change occurs
through class struggle; and that the capitalist system will inevitably
wither away to be superseded by a classless society.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Marxism-Leninism</ent>⟦br⟧
